OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FAre you content or concerned about the
OL,7,Fhealth service here in Wales? Do you
OL,8,Flike or loathe the transport system?
OL,9,FDo you have strong feelings about how
OL,10,Fschools are performing or even the
OL,11,Fbuildings that house them? If you want
OL,12,Fto have a say on those and lots of
OL,13,Fother public services, then this
OL,14,Felection is your chance.
OL,16,FAll of the things above are devolved;
OL,17,Fin other words, responsibility for
OL,18,Fthem lies with the Senedd, or Welsh
OL,19,FParliament, and the Welsh Government
OL,20,Fin Cardiff, not the UK Parliament in
OL,21,FWestminster.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
