OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FSenedd members can make and change
OL,7,Flaws in all the devolved areas,
OL,8,Factions that are led by the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment, which is made up of Senedd
OL,10,Fmembers but is separate to the
OL,11,Fparliament itself. The Welsh
OL,12,FGovernment's budget is #27bn next year.
OL,14,FThat means the election on 7 May is
OL,15,Fimportant in itself but it's also
OL,16,Fhugely significant in other ways.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
