PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FFor a start, a huge amount is
OL,7,Fchanging. We'll be electing 96 Senedd
OL,8,FMembers to represent us in Cardiff
OL,9,FBay, an increase on the 60 that there
OL,10,Fhave been since devolution began in
OL,11,F1999.
OL,13,FThe way that we elect them is changing
OL,14,Ftoo.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FA new electoral system has been
OL,7,Fintroduced that's considered to be
OL,8,Fmore proportional. In other words,
OL,9,Fthat reflects more fairly the way that
OL,10,Feverybody votes. Instead of each
OL,11,Fconstituency being represented by one
OL,12,Fperson who wins with a straight
OL,13,Fmajority, each of those constituencies
OL,14,Fwill have six members from different
OL,15,Fparties.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThe constituencies are different.
OL,7,FThere are 16 and they're much larger,
OL,8,Fbased on the boundaries of two
OL,9,FWestminster constituencies and with
OL,10,Fsingle Welsh-only names such as
OL,11,FCaerdydd Ffynon Taf or Fflint Wrecsam.
OL,13,FThere's a difference in casting votes.
OL,14,FWe'll be given a single ballot paper
OL,15,Fand asked to choose one party or an
OL,16,Findependent candidate.
OL,18,FThose votes are then added up and
OL,19,Fdivided using a system known as the
OL,20,FD'Hondt method to select six winners
OL,21,Fin each constituency.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FOne effect of these changes will be
OL,7,Fthat it's extremely unlikely that any
OL,8,Fparty will win enough Senedd seats to
OL,9,Fform a government on its own. It's
OL,10,Fmuch more likely that parties will
OL,11,Fhave to reach deals, informal or
OL,12,Fformal, in order to make a government
OL,13,Ffeasible.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FAdd into all this change the fact that
OL,7,Fit now seems certain that there'll be
OL,8,Fa radical political upheaval. Our
OL,9,Fpolls have consistently shown that
OL,10,FLabour has become unpopular with
OL,11,Fvoters and could be on course to lose
OL,12,Fpower. If that were to happen, it
OL,13,Fwould be unprecedented - Labour has
OL,14,Fbeen in power in Cardiff since
OL,15,Fdevolution began. Going further back,
OL,16,Fthe party has been the largest party
OL,17,Fin Wales in every election for a
OL,18,Fhundred years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FThe same polls show that the two
OL,7,Ffrontrunners to take over are Plaid
OL,8,FCymru and Reform UK. Plaid Cymru has
OL,9,Fnever performed this well in polls in
OL,10,Fits history - our latest survey
OL,11,Fsuggested the party could win enough
OL,12,Fseats to attempt to govern alone as a
OL,13,Fminority government.
OL,15,FReform UK had only just formed from
OL,16,Fthe ashes of the Brexit Party and UKIP
OL,17,Fat the time of the last election in
OL,18,F2021. To have come from nothing to
OL,19,Fbeing in second place in five years is
OL,20,Fextraordinary.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FMuch of its success seems to be coming
OL,7,Fat the expense of the Conservatives,
OL,8,Fwho, the polls suggest, have gone from
OL,9,Ftheir best-ever Senedd Election in
OL,10,F2021 to a point where they could end
OL,11,Fup with less than a handful of seats.
OL,13,FThis could also be the moment for the
OL,14,FGreen Party, which could finally take
OL,15,Fits place in the Senedd. The Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats are hoping to have more than
OL,17,Fthe single seat they've had for the
OL,18,Flast ten years, but the signs aren't
OL,19,Fgreat.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1775736665
OL,3,CChange is coming: Everything you need
OL,4,Cto know about the Senedd Election
OL,6,FAll of this comes with a health
OL,7,Fwarning: polls are snapshots and
OL,8,Fthings change suddenly in election
OL,9,Fcampaigns. What's more, the new
OL,10,Felectoral system makes outcomes very
OL,11,Fdifficult to predict because very
OL,12,Fsmall numbers of votes could mean the
OL,13,Fdifference between winning some of the
OL,14,Ffifth and sixth place seats or not.
OL,16,FBut change is on its way to Welsh
OL,17,Fpolitics; potentially radical change,
OL,18,Fpotentially historic change. What
OL,19,Fshape that change takes is down to all
OL,20,Fof us on 7 May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
